        "description": "Legency Remedies Pvt Ltd is a leading Medical Device CE, ISO 13485, MDSAP, MDL approved for Sodium Chloride 0.9% w/v  and Pharmaceutical WHO GMP  (Small volume parentals - Injectables and Nebules ) manufacturer based in Baddi District, Solan, India. Our 2000 sqm facility has been designed in compliance with several international regulations and holds a variety of certifications for global exports. Small Volume Manufacturing siteWith our state of the art automatic production lines and procurement process, we supply over 10 Million ampoules per month to companies both locally and globally under OEM, Private Labels and Contract Manufacturing. We offer various formulations approved as a Medical Device for the European, Canadian, United Kingdom and other international markets. At our current manufacturing site for small volume formulations we offer a range of Medical Devices under the current MDD certification through our Notified Body - DQS, we will begin supplying under the new MDR certification approved by TUV in December 2025.  1.Sodium Chloride 0.9% w/v - Medical Device for three intended uses: Irrigation, Eyewash & Inhalation (MDD Certification)          2ml, 2.5ml, 3ml, 3.5ml, 5ml, 10ml, 15ml, 20ml, 25ml, 30ml2.Sucrose 24% oral solution without preservatives 1ml & 2ml - Non-pharmacological comfort measure for babies3.Sodium Chloride 0.9% w/v - Medical Device covering a range of intended uses : Irrigation & Inhalation, Physiological / Multipurpose saline, Topical Irrigation / Isotonic Saline (MDR Certification)2ml, 2.5ml, 3ml, 3.5ml, 5ml, 10ml, 15ml, 20ml, 25ml, 30ml, 50ml, 60ml, 100ml, 120mlSecond Manufacturing Facility - 5 production lines of various packing styles & compositions (Launch date MDR: Q3 2026 - Medical device formulations)Prefilled syringes: 2ml, 3ml, 5ml, 10mlAerosol Spray Bag on Valve technology : 50ml, 100ml, 125ml, 150ml, 200ml, 250mlSachets: 20ml, 25ml, 30ml, 50ml, 100mlThree piece dropsMetered Dose Inhalers (MDI)\nLegency Remedies has started its' new expansion project to house a second facility under our umbrella with a larger portfolio of Medical Devices under the new MDR and Medicines range. At our new site, we shall house a variety of different packing styles in various compositions to provide our customers with larger choices to suit their needs. At our second site we will also offer our customers Private Labels, OEM and Contract Manufacturing Options. Research & Development OpportunitiesOur team at Legency Remedies Pvt Ltd enjoys to explore, discover and innovate. If your company has a new product formulation that matches any of our current or upcoming packing styles or even a pre-existing product that you would like to explore together with us, it would be our pleasure to support your ideas to commercialization. Medica 2025 - InvitationWe are ecstatic to share our product range, our upcoming facility and new compositions with you during Medica 2025. From our team to yours, we are looking forward to hosting you at our booth and exploring the possibilities we can achieve together over a cup of Indian Chai or Coffee and some lovely Treats from home! We are certain that our current product profile and upcoming facility meets your expectations of quality and standard.On our profile you will be able to view our offered compositions in our videos.If you may have any questions before the fair or after, please do not hesitate to reach out to us at: sales@legencyremedies.com / legency.remedies@rediffmail.com. Please do visit our stall for further details on our product composition list with our knowledgeable and experienced team. We look forward to seeing you at Medica Exhibition 2025. We wish you a lovely Medica 2025 Exhibition!",
