        "description": "TRUST TRADITION. EXPERIENCE INNOVATION For more than 50 years, PAJUNK® has stood for innovative medical technology Made in Germany.The Pajunk Group is an internationally operating and owner-run company with headquarters in Geisingen, Baden-Württemberg, and sales offices in Atlanta (USA), Newcastle (UK) and Baar (CH).Pajunk's success story began in the mid-1960s in Baden-Württemberg, the cradle of precision engineering. It was here that the brothers Horst and Heinrich Pajunk laid the foundation stone for the company, which is dedicated to the development and manufacture of high-precision medical technology instruments. Since 1993, Simone Pajunk-Schelling and Martin Hauger have managed the company in the second generation. Under their joint management, the internationalisation of Pajunk was successfully advanced, but always with a clear reference to the regional production site in Geisingen (Germany).Since then, the family-owned company has grown steadily and now employs over 600 people worldwide. Pajunk has specialised in the production of needles in the medical field and is also considered the inventor of the atraumatic needle - the SPROTTE®.Today, the main sales of Pajunk products are in the sectors of Regional Anaesthesia, Pain Management, Neurorehabilitation & Neurology, Biopsy as well as Minimally Invasive Surgery.With the claim \"Trust Tradition. Experience Innovation\", Pajunk makes a promise of quality, reliability and safety. The focus is always on the future, which is why Pajunk is already working today on innovative solutions for tomorrow. By this innovation always remains tradition.",
